{"title":"肚子里使劲","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚子里使劲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好小子！这回算你行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我嚜‘相当主观’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我嚜‘拒绝批评’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有什么‘压制’‘报复’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么难听！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你居然当着众人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没大没小"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（桌子上啪的一声）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——批评了一顿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼，老子革命的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还在桌子底下爬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，这回你逞能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出了风头，可是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你小心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子要叫你瞧瞧颜色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要弄得你走头无路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家宅不安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡犬不宁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当然啰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（脑袋在空中转了一圈）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回，哼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只在肚子里使劲……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（嘴角边浮起一丝笑影）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一番话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没有说出声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是心里面暗暗地念叨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，这些想法"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽则痛快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却见不得人！（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华君武插图"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}